  "detailed_description": "<strong>Neon Ninja: Pixel Slasher is an adrenaline-pumping cyberpunk action game with a pixelated twist!</strong><br><br>Destroy your enemies to the beat of stylish music, dodging traps and lasers!<br><br>Master the art of quick jumping to avoid falling into spikey traps!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/fb5019c704b0987bd41a5b612bd699f9.poster.avif?t=1704211268\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/fb5019c704b0987bd41a5b612bd699f9.webm?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/fb5019c704b0987bd41a5b612bd699f9.mp4?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Run from deadly bosses destroying everything on their way!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/8b3dfb8fd15327c075adfa98f98ff848.poster.avif?t=1704211268\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/8b3dfb8fd15327c075adfa98f98ff848.webm?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/8b3dfb8fd15327c075adfa98f98ff848.mp4?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Break into guarded hideouts, eliminate the enemies and collect rare artifacts!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/ddb82bbcb20502f4b8680e5ceb56a5e0.poster.avif?t=1704211268\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/ddb82bbcb20502f4b8680e5ceb56a5e0.webm?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/ddb82bbcb20502f4b8680e5ceb56a5e0.mp4?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect shurikens on your way to attack your enemies from distance!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/5c327865d8ff9b5e6bf257d0c029ca25.poster.avif?t=1704211268\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/5c327865d8ff9b5e6bf257d0c029ca25.webm?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/5c327865d8ff9b5e6bf257d0c029ca25.mp4?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Jump on walls to get to hard to reach secret locations!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/be70141782cbf1503cf8de9f225ce093.poster.avif?t=1704211268\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/be70141782cbf1503cf8de9f225ce093.webm?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618100/extras/be70141782cbf1503cf8de9f225ce093.mp4?t=1704211268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready to immerse yourself in a pixelated cyberpunk world with dangerous opponents and a dystopian future civilization? <br>Welcome to Neon Ninja: Pixel Slasher! Fans of classic platformers and runners worldwide surely won’t be disappointed by joining this game - a vast cyberpunk world, full of brutal battles for survival and freedom!<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Experience the driving gameplay<br></li><li> Addictive retro autorunner game<br></li><li> Simple three-button controls<br></li><li> Aggressive music for quick kills<br></li><li> Enjoy the incredible pixel graphics of the cyberpunk world<br></li><li> Improve your skills and reaction, fight and progress through new levels</li></ul>",
